---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms & Conditions — TaxDebtWealthSuite"
  description="Terms and conditions for utilizing the TaxDebtWealthSuite calculation suite, including disclaimer of warranties and intellectual property rights."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-between">
    
    <!-- Top Navigation Header -->
    <header class="border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/80 backdrop-blur-md sticky top-0 z-50">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between h-16 sm:h-20">
          
          <!-- Logo & Branding -->
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <a href="/" class="flex items-center space-x-3 hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-tr from-brand-600 to-accent-emerald flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/20">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h1 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white font-sans">
                  TaxDebtWealth<span class="text-brand-400">Suite</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 hidden sm:block">Advanced Strategic Finance Suite</p>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Navigation Links / CTA -->
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
            <a href="/" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all focus-ring text-xs font-semibold flex items-center space-x-1.5">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
              </svg>
              <span>Back to Calculators</span>
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content Container -->
    <main class="flex-grow max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 sm:py-16">
      
      <!-- Back Link for Mobile/SEO -->
      <div class="mb-8">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300 transition-colors">
          &larr; Back to Calculators
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Article Base -->
      <article class="space-y-8">
        <header class="border-b border-slate-800 pb-6">
          <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight font-sans">Terms & Conditions</h1>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2">Last Updated: June 25, 2026</p>
        </header>

        <!-- Section 1 -->
        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            By accessing or using TaxDebtWealthSuite (located at this domain), you agree to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you are prohibited from using our calculators, sheets, or content.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 2 -->
        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide">2. Permitted Personal Use</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            You are granted a non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to access and use our interactive calculators (Buy, Borrow, Die; Side-Hustle Tax Predictor; and Debt payoff planner) strictly for personal, non-commercial, and educational evaluation. 
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            You agree not to scrape, reverse engineer, copy, or redistribute the source code, algorithms, logic, or formulas underlying our client-side modules without explicit written consent from the administrators of TaxDebtWealthSuite.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 3 -->
        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide">3. Disclaimer of Warranties & Estimates</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            The calculations, outcomes, reports, and tax assessments generated by TaxDebtWealthSuite are mathematical approximations based on user-supplied variables and standard legislative formulas. They are provided on an <strong>"as-is" and "as-available" basis</strong>.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed text-amber-300">
            <strong>CRITICAL:</strong> TaxDebtWealthSuite makes no warranties, expressed or implied, regarding the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of tax brackets, national insurance estimates, blended APR timelines, or SBLOC liquidation margins. Tax codes and interest rates change frequently. You should never make capital structures, debt repayment decisions, or leveraged borrowing decisions based solely on these tools. Consult a qualified professional advisor.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 4 -->
        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide">4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            In no event shall TaxDebtWealthSuite, its developers, or its affiliates be liable for any damages (including, without limitation, damages for loss of capital, tax penalties, margin calls, or business interruption) arising out of the use or inability to use the mathematical calculators, even if we have been notified orally or in writing of the possibility of such damage.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 5 -->
        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            All design systems, UI components, custom formulas, dynamic charts, scripts, and written guides present on this site are the intellectual property of TaxDebtWealthSuite and are protected by applicable copyright and trademark laws.
          </p>
        </section>
      </article>

    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="border-t border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/90 py-10 text-xs text-slate-400">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-6">
          <!-- Copyright & Disclaimer info -->
          <div class="max-w-xl space-y-2">
            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-300">
              &copy; 2026 TaxDebtWealthSuite. All rights reserved.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              Disclaimer: The calculators provided on this website are for informational and educational purposes only and do not constitute professional financial or legal advice.
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Legal & Info links -->
          <nav class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-slate-400" aria-label="Footer Navigation">
            <a href="/about" class="hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium">About Us</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium">Contact Us</a>
            <a href="/privacy-policy" class="hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium">Privacy Policy</a>
            <a href="/terms-conditions" class="hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium">Terms & Conditions</a>
          </nav>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-slate-900 pt-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-2 text-slate-600">
          <p>Calculations are estimates. All financial strategies contain risk.</p>
          <p>Hosted on Cloudflare Pages.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </div>
</Layout>
